data.text:
Like most websites, we use cookies to make sure our site works the way you expect it to, improve your experience on our site, analyze site usage, and assist in our marketing efforts. By choosing “Accept”, you agree to the storing of all categories of cookies on your device. You can manage your cookie settings under “Preferences”. You can find more information in our privacy policy. We use cookies to improve your experience while you navigate through the website. Among the cookies we use, some are categorized as necessary as they are essential for the working of basic functionalities of the website and are stored on your browser. We also use third-party cookies that help us analyze, understand how you use this website and assist in our marketing efforts in order to improve your experience. These cookies will be stored in your browser only with your consent. You can withdraw your consent for these cookies at any time on our Privacy Policy site.

Necessary These cookies are essential for you to browse our website and use its features. These cookies will generally be first-party session cookies, but can also be generated by third parties. This is for example the case when an essential feature of our website relies on an external tool (e.g. contacting customer service via our Help Center).

Analytics These cookies collect information about how users use our website, such as which pages they visited and which links they clicked on. These cookies are from third-party analytics services and are for the exclusive use of the owner of the website.

Advertisement These cookies track your online activity to help advertisers deliver more relevant advertising. These cookies can share that information with other organizations or advertisers. These are persistent cookies and almost always of third-party provenance.
